{"tid":1023713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係曼聯新7號！咁山神點算呀","createTime":"2019-02-16T04:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T05:46:31.000Z","uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"875a302195e7a73d47f3f701ca071617dddb93a9","tid":1023713,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"16歲艾米恩斯天才新星艾美蘭喺Instagram有圖有真相自爆，已經完成轉會正式加盟曼聯，但最離奇係，佢得到印住自己個名嘅紅魔7號波衫簽約，搞到有網民問，阿歷斯山齊士係咪確定要離隊收擋喎！ <br />\n<br />\n艾美蘭最佳位置係翼鋒，踢法有啲似曼城嘅利萊辛尼，佢本身係法國U16成員，比利時國家隊都想嗌佢過檔加入，而且祖雲達斯同巴黎聖日耳門都想搶人，最後佢決定去奧脫福，搞到有網民話，如果佢真係掂，不妨直接上一隊取代山神。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，有網友好抵死咁話：「有冇人話畀山齊士知，佢冇咗件7號波衫？」雖然好多曼迷希望，艾美蘭勁到可以代替山神，但之前有消息話，其實紅魔打算將佢借返番畀艾米恩斯，等佢有更多機會磨練，或者球迷要畀多啲時間佢爭取上位呀！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190216/mobile/bkn-20190216111643158-0216_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190216%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190216111643158-0216_00882_001.html&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=f757b85d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190216/mobile/bkn-20190216111643158-0216_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d948c2a468dd5cc92a2858335d8d7fdc6c230d05","tid":1023713,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b857ac2f0e5d9bbe3791971c4a9b33ab407331","tid":1023713,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"多頭髮過樓主"},{"pid":"9572ad18261ce7a03e9e6b96710ab6734fbe0c35","tid":1023713,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"山狗真係不得善終"},{"pid":"68eec2acb8b273c9d89031052fb98a63fa8f336b","tid":1023713,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b857ac2f0e5d9bbe3791971c4a9b33ab407331","tid":1023713,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:18:12.